        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">An instance belonging to the class should be rather inferred as asserted.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">tensile strength in the rolling direction</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Tensile strength in to the rolling direction is a tensile strength which is measured on a sample cut parallel to the rolling direction.</skos:definition>
